Interface ContentFolder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Synthetic
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExcludeFolder, SourceFolder, UserDefinedExcludeFolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContentFolderBaseImpl, JpsContentFolderBase, JpsExcludeFolder, JpsSourceFolder, SourceFolderImpl

    public interface ContentFolder
extends Synthetic
    Represents a source or exclude root under the content root of a module.
    See Also:
    ContentEntry.getSourceFolders(), ContentEntry.getExcludeFolders()
